Which function correctly adds a given integer to each element and returns the modified list? Select the correct answer.
```dart
// A
List<int> addToList(List<int> list, int addition) {
  for (int number in list) {
    number += addition;
  }
  return list;
}

// B
List<int> addToList(List<int> list, int addition) {
  for (int element of list) {
    element = element + addition;
  }
  return list;
}

// C
List<int> addToList(List<int> list, int addition) {
  for (int i = 0; i <= list.length; i++) {
    list[i] += addition;
  }
  return list;
}

// D
List<int> addToList(List<int> list, int addition) {
  for (int i = 0; i < list.length; i = i + 1) {
    list[i] = list[i] + addition;
  }
  return list;
}
```

